    "name": "A Simple Ball Game",
    "steam_appid": 3281330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/b74e248128060aaa2715fe9c218a1a2a.poster.avif?t=1758037808\" width=600 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/b74e248128060aaa2715fe9c218a1a2a.webm?t=1758037808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/d73a0ccc1631d92d2fdd233eaa08d19f.webp?t=1758037808\" width=615 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>A Simple Ball Game</strong>, lead our spherical friend, the ball, through tricky pathways and  moving obstacles to finally reach the goal. Each level is a sandbox full of possibilities, many with unconventional or hidden shortcuts to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is all about creativity, so it is up to you to decide how to approach each challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/f12d260b7052ef88a90ea9a3756ed8fc.poster.avif?t=1758037808\" width=600 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/f12d260b7052ef88a90ea9a3756ed8fc.webm?t=1758037808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/8175b5707d3c66a6cfca2a449d71f4c2.webp?t=1758037808\" width=615 height=60 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80 challenging stages that will push your creativity and platforming skills to the limit. From narrow pathways and downward spirals, to sprawling puzzle-box contraptions, no two stages are quite the same.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Challenge Mode, take on the gauntlet of stages back to back.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Rogue Mode, even a simple mistake could cost you the run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Practice Mode, learn each level inside out and hone your ball rolling prowess.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect all the artifacts to unlock a set of extra stages that will really test your ball rolling abilities. There's one hidden somewhere on each level, so keep a look out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look your spherical best with over 60 visual  modifications for your ball. Try out different combinations and colors to create your own uniquely  smooth style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete hidden achievements and unlock rare customizations for your ball.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With three styles of play: controller, mouse, and keyboard, approach the game any way you like. For maximum precision, A CONTROLLER IS HIGHLY RECOMMENDED.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/23e77b88f6cee8f11f6ecf0dea5f0888.poster.avif?t=1758037808\" width=600 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/23e77b88f6cee8f11f6ecf0dea5f0888.webm?t=1758037808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
